{"tid":2073524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得而家對巴士司機有啲逆向歧視","createTime":"2020-06-21T11:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T08:52:17.000Z","uid":182885,"like":41,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5a68c604ae31d626cb4d4a1403951588f871cb95","tid":2073524,"uid":182885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"唔知標題有冇錯意思，純討論<br />\n<br />\n我想講係呢一兩年，巴士司機呢個職業好似受到過份保護，大概由大埔公路意外之後<br />\n<br />\n而家巴士司機好似完全唔驚人投訴，甚至好多司機夠膽屌返個客，當然有啲客係抵屌，但我見感覺係多左好多串柒柒的巴士司機<br />\n<br />\n點解我咁諗，因為近排試過3次總站上車，司機係遲4-5分鐘開車，當然你去廁所，或塞車遲返要遲開無問題，但我見2次係係旁邊扯埋枝煙，或者繼續煲劇/打機所以遲開車，咁我唔趕，無所謂爭個少少，有一次，我前面嗰後生仔問一問點解遲開（態度正常），個巴士司機即刻話你唔滿意可以去投訴，我心諗CLS，洗唔洗咁樣挑人機，2個就嗌交了，最癲係個巴士司機話個後生唔好挑釁佢情緒，否則佢覺得唔適合繼續揸車，大家等下一架<br />\n<br />\n我當堂呆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排又係facebook d group 見有司機出post有人唔禁鐘就唔停車（大站），係，啲乘客係抵死唔禁鐘，但又同客鬧交又出post 講晒粗口屌9啲客，其實有乜為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3339c91d0031ceda56ab60ea6b554e297670f22a","tid":2073524,"uid":132587,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"一路都係人既問題<br />\n巴士佬態度不嬲都唔係好<br />\n但我都遇過好多nice既"},{"pid":"f16a3575f4d75e621bffbe74fa88e7ba8745b182","tid":2073524,"uid":295230,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"其實係香港人既性格問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1a6c525442302262b095244493285c81c4705a","tid":2073524,"uid":251614,"like":53,"dislike":6,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"冇人禁鐘唔停大站有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09468d67cffece0f1f4ef1fbd6b6bd5eaf19eb9","tid":2073524,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫遲開車，渣完成粒鐘  返嚟煲枝煙都唔得？"},{"pid":"24e5396c9f36c1fa20add984497bd9c5ca01d9e0","tid":2073524,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"比幾蚊就咁多嘢講<br />\n趕時間坐的士啦"},{"pid":"5685b188d41d7fe6aeec26f4e631a4241f31967d","tid":2073524,"uid":9193,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"cd1a6c525442302262b095244493285c81c4705a","tid":2073524,"uid":251614,"like":53,"dislike":6,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:42.000Z","msg":"冇人禁鐘唔停大站有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"除咗必停站諗唔到唔撳鐘點解要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3129996f32b93dcee49676e6409c8b578382c6","tid":2073524,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e09468d67cffece0f1f4ef1fbd6b6bd5eaf19eb9","tid":2073524,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫遲開車，渣完成粒鐘  返嚟煲枝煙都唔得？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"問果個肯定係mon撚住個app果d毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲幾分鐘就屌人脫班遲開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1deae9e18140f449d976446c3562c4367bd29b","tid":2073524,"uid":116390,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"e09468d67cffece0f1f4ef1fbd6b6bd5eaf19eb9","tid":2073524,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫遲開車，渣完成粒鐘  返嚟煲枝煙都唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"巴士有固定開車時間<br />\n你早左返煲成包煙都冇問題<br />\n你遲左返仲係側邊慢慢食<br />\n仲要串9返個客就有問題"},{"pid":"975d6017b0c36514297c5c0996786975634996c6","tid":2073524,"uid":192327,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"不如掉返轉咁諗 <br />\n點解要屌鳩巴士佬 屌鳩黨鐵 的士佬 但你唔敢屌鳩Van仔佬<br />\n係佢服務唔到你 定 你覺得唔值 定 你係發洩 定你欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"c33ea7688da9c0f9a1ba8162d289a9d374eeed38","tid":2073524,"uid":123456,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e09468d67cffece0f1f4ef1fbd6b6bd5eaf19eb9","tid":2073524,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫遲開車，渣完成粒鐘  返嚟煲枝煙都唔得？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遲過原定鐘數咪叫遲開囉<br />\n你準時開到<br />\n我話鳩知你渣完叫雞出火咩</span>"},{"pid":"40212632d21cdf78bb296f51e0b5f8e77d1f3cbd","tid":2073524,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"975d6017b0c36514297c5c0996786975634996c6","tid":2073524,"uid":192327,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"不如掉返轉咁諗 <br />\n點解要屌鳩巴士佬 屌鳩黨鐵 的士佬 但你唔敢屌鳩Van仔佬<br />\n係佢服務唔到你 定 你覺得唔值 定 你係發洩 定你欺善怕惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"着住制服咪好恰啲囉"},{"pid":"c66797503c9a198c9add565921dcc2e3de96cc28","tid":2073524,"uid":294343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係，你投訴巴士公司，上面有上面覆下面有下面做，你投訴甩車，上面就話改，結果都係甩幾十分鐘"},{"pid":"4dd5ef463bfa7334d492f65b76118f00be5c06de","tid":2073524,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxJRgtEbOio&amp;t=1145s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQxJRgtEbOio%26t%3D1145s&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2YwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=e4aabddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxJRgtEbOio&amp;t=1145s</a><br />\n<br />\n不嬲都屌客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854c0115b628c256ff5605fd66a9138349fe4d2a","tid":2073524,"uid":274722,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"因為揸巴士份工咁西佢冇野好輸,佢年資唔高既咪去第二間揸車<br />\n<br />\n要專心揸車<br />\n工作期間冇得玩電話，大塞車都要on99坐係度<br />\n又要做幾十個客既cs<br />\n<br />\n一個月兩萬都冇，燥底正常"},{"pid":"237c756bf05e3d9bc9c23a1e96ad9158ac52f1f5","tid":2073524,"uid":294343,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"仲有呀，香港人係咁容易俾風向吹。樓主講中埔單嘢，之後個女司機出尼，成個網上風向覺得佢女人仔好勁好勇，好同情佢。<br />\n<br />\n但你睇返 全世界都關注緊巴士安全，佢係爭取加人工炸，當正自己人民英雄，結果證明佢自己係一個貪錢死藍絲"},{"pid":"f94561276254f80c86944a2aa8fc370e09e9a642","tid":2073524,"uid":197563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"巴膠中意含巴士狗啫<br />\n唔使咁上心喎"},{"pid":"605998fa5bb21cb68085e25f96f08187b5faf559","tid":2073524,"uid":66,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3339c91d0031ceda56ab60ea6b554e297670f22a","tid":2073524,"uid":132587,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"一路都係人既問題<br />\n巴士佬態度不嬲都唔係好<br />\n但我都遇過好多nice既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n試過遇到個司機<br />\n等我坐低先開車<br />\n驚我企唔穩會跌死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申個陣得我一個試車<br />\n佢可以見我拍完卡即時踩油"},{"pid":"5d79aa4660fdbef144c4a413fdc9967b08c6dc05","tid":2073524,"uid":215611,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"何謂大站？<br />\n每人把呎都唔同<br />\n睇鐘就係最好指示"},{"pid":"991fcdb7d7a7537a17c08c4ba3853ce10fe76506","tid":2073524,"uid":215501,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e09468d67cffece0f1f4ef1fbd6b6bd5eaf19eb9","tid":2073524,"uid":75137,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"咩叫遲開車，渣完成粒鐘  返嚟煲枝煙都唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n站長隨時改開車時間都得<br />\n架車遲咗返黎比幾分鐘師傅抖好正常"},{"pid":"ddf0be297908ef17108a2168d5b5f01056b69084","tid":2073524,"uid":161417,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"依家d巴士司機有光環唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過個見個巴士司機屌個乘客唔企入去<br />\n但係架車滿到仆街下層d人根本郁唔到<br />\n個乘客